iati-activity.description: RRM is an important tool for responding to disaster. It allows SRC and the RC/RC Movement to have a flexible and rapid response to emergencies worldwide. In 2011 SRC was granted for SEK 42.1 million for Minor Emergencies frame,including administrative costs.Through the RRM, SRC aims to indirectly reach millions of people affected by suddenonset humanitarian crises in 2011.
